<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I would get an ivy etched cords, (+5 wis, 4 ac) NOT a lizzy mantle, which only has 3 wis. I would also get Chipped Bone Bracers insted of Polished, because CBBs have more wisdom and armor class. Also, the wisdom earrings you are referring to are THREE wisdom earrings, not four. There's no such thing as 4 wi earrings. Also, if you have the cash, I'd get a Mammoth Cloak, and Gatorscale Legs. You definately cannot afford 15k - 20k for Golden Efreeti Boots.</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
