<tr>
<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">You really want maximum bang for your buck so... you can get + 6 WIS rings from your friendly jeweller for about 225pp each - that's + 12 WIS for 450pp. Next get + 3 WIS earrings for 20 - 25pp each, Then a Savant's Cap for about 40pp will give you + 3 WIS and + 3 INT. I would then get a Silver Ruby Vail (sic) for 165pp, which gives you + 4 WIS and + 4 STR. In all, for an outlay of approx 700pp you can get a WIS increase of 25!! Compare that with a Chipped Bone Bracer, which gives you + 3 WIS for about 450pp. Buy smart and get the most WIS for your money - buy the more esoteric items when you can afford them.</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
